<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.5">
<l>appa ṉēyaṭa lāḻiyāṉē yāḻkaṭa laikkaṭainta</l>
<l>tuppa ṉēyuṉ ṟōḷka ṇāṉkuṅ kaṇṭiṭakkūṭuṅ koleṉṟu</l>
<l>eppo ḻutuṅ kaṇṇa nīrkoṇ ṭāvi tuvarntuvarntu</l>
<l>ippō ḻutē vanti ṭāyeṉ ṟēḻaiyē ṉōkkuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Father, you with the murderous discus, when will it be possible to see</l>
<l>your four shoulders, mighty one who churned the deep ocean?</l>
<l>All the time wiping [and] wiping [my] soul with eye water</l>
<l>wretched me will look [at you], saying “this one time, come.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
